editorialNotes.standard: Pixelmator sets a new standard for photo editing on iPhone and iPad with a suite of staggeringly powerful tools. Plus, with seamless syncing using iCloud Drive, it doesn’t matter where the project was started—you can keep editing on your iPhone, iPad, or Mac.
